data.description: Spectacular opportunity to scoop up a Townhouse in the lovely Knox Woods. An end unit to boot. Enjoy the changing seasons on your freshly painted deck with the peaceful view of your tree lined yard. Head inside for  the perfect opportunity to curl up with a good book or your favorite movie, sit back and enjoy the crackling of the wood burning fireplace. Upstairs has a large landing where you could set up an office space, reading nook, or maybe yoga? So many great uses for that space. In the basement you'll notice a nearly complete added bonus room. Just finish painting and add flooring. This community is equipped with Pools and Tennis Courts for added fun and convenience. (small fee for the year) The Roof and Fascia recently replaced 11/23. HOA $190 Monthly.
